<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-7292] Metrics 2 TestSinkQueue is racy</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-7292</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The TestSinkQueue is racy (Thread.yield is not enough to guarantee other intended thread getting run), though it&apos;s the first time (from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-7289&quot; title=&quot;ivy: test conf should not extend common conf&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HADOOP-7289&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HADOOP-7289&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) I saw it manifested here.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
